    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点是Retail_OrderManagement指向EmptyLot。那EmptyLot之后的状态怎么流转？是车辆进入后直接到PartiallyFull吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmptyLot",
        "PartiallyFull",
        "Park vehicle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，EmptyLot描述为\"No vehicles parked\"，车辆进入后变为PartiallyFull。PartiallyFull是\"Some slots occupied\"，继续停车会到Full状态，也就是\"All slots occupied\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmptyLot",
        "PartiallyFull",
        "Full",
        "No vehicles parked",
        "Some slots occupied",
        "All slots occupied"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把三个主要状态画好了，流转关系是EmptyLot到PartiallyFull再到Full，都是Park vehicle触发。那车辆离开呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmptyLot",
        "PartiallyFull",
        "Full",
        "Park vehicle",
        "Remove vehicle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "车辆离开用Remove vehicle触发，Full可以回到PartiallyFull，PartiallyFull可以回到EmptyLot。另外三个状态都要能进入Maintenance模式，触发条件是Enter maintenance mode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Full",
        "PartiallyFull",
