      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Maintenance有两个出口：Reset lot回到EmptyLot，Restore previous state回到PartiallyFull，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Maintenance",
        "EmptyLot",
